{"tid":319312,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"［教精你］想要錢既DSE雞入黎睇","createTime":"2017-07-12T16:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T17:06:36.000Z","uid":73492,"like":21,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7b810333142e75570581509992f8d8ab2f5f51f","tid":319312,"uid":73492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:36:39.000Z","msg":"唔咒你班傻撚入樹仁住 今日興之所至教下你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你讀書為錢，跟實我下面個flow選科，你明年今日會多謝我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nA 醫學》牙醫》獸醫》除護理外 五寶》護理<br />\nB 建築》土木工程》測量》屋宇設備工程／社工<br />\nC 法律／精算》機械工程／機電工程／電子工程／電腦科學》幼兒教育》除幼教外 所有教育學科<br />\n<br />\nD 會計／英文／心理<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔應該入既科有以下兩種：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n伏：所有BBA科（包括QFIN／RISK MAN／MKT），酒店管理，測繪，營養<br />\n<br />\n超級大伏：所有文科，所有社科，所有純科學，所有設計／歌影視相關學科<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留意點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1：學科重要過校名 係重要一百倍左右 至於同一專科比較下就可以再鬥校名<br />\n<br />\n2：所有ABC系列既學科，係叫做為錢而選，而無考慮難度。事實上，入面大部份科需要既專業知識水平極高，即係要讀撚到你仆街，特別係醫學，建築，法律，可能讀到損害身體，呢個係要錢定要身體既問題 你諗你。<br />\n<br />\n3：D系列既科，其實同ABC系列既搵食能力有距離，要選就三思<br />\n<br />\n4：其實有好多科無講，EG一大堆工程學分支，不過實在唔可以話呢堆科搵食／話呢堆科伏，所以唔特別提<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母有父幹既話可以當我成篇文係垃圾，你開心選科就好。"},{"pid":"0f1118cb0a981684efcf48e312781981e97fc667","tid":319312,"uid":73492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26445f6a403d935f17ced64e4ed0f18c61b3b3e0","tid":319312,"uid":73492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a8739f858c34db0ffcf37b14e360663277639fa","tid":319312,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T17:09:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1：學科重要過校名 係重要一百倍左右 至於同一專科比較下就可以再鬥校名</blockquote><br />\n東大醫療&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;港大徙銀紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80af62c65804a2dfdd79f284812fbca77ea87b77","tid":319312,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T19:04:49.000Z","msg":"好難得入到黎唔屌柒你，仲會擺低正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次真心高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f2e5ab2b39620db8826c4f7959ee6a565a752a","tid":319312,"uid":19388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T19:09:02.000Z","msg":"Archi&gt;civil?"},{"pid":"4ccff575f64d11e28afda71110f3bb6120a9ba44","tid":319312,"uid":119379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T19:19:26.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"8660c0005fec3614c2a8cb4f04e38d59d0abd541","tid":319312,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T19:24:49.000Z","msg":"教育咁高？"},{"pid":"b819550047602eb8aac1eae836d5f356b3be7ee5","tid":319312,"uid":73492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5711e92e6d393bcd11c9dae946891924237eead7","tid":319312,"uid":73492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T03:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"149afc1ef33e06e3736f2182bebe634a67f09c66","tid":319312,"uid":73492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12